OL,6,FA former surgeon who carried out
OL,7,F"unsafe" and "unsanitary"
OL,8,Fcircumcisions as part of a private
OL,9,Fmobile service has been jailed.
OL,11,FDr Mohammad Siddiqui, 58, from
OL,12,FBirmingham, provided the service
OL,13,Fwhilst working as a clinical fellow in
OL,14,Fpaediatric surgery at University
OL,15,FHospital Southampton NHS Foundation
OL,16,FTrust, between June 2012 and November
OL,17,F2013.
OL,19,FHe was able to source the anaesthetic
OL,20,FBupivacaine Hydrochloride which is a
OL,21,Fprescription only medication.
