OL,3,CFormer surgeon carried out 'unsafe'
OL,4,Ccircumcisions as part of mobile service
OL,6,FHe's now been jailed for a combined
OL,7,Ftotal of more than five and-a-half
OL,8,Fyears, following a long-running
OL,9,Finvestigation led by Hampshire and
OL,10,FIsle of Wight Constabulary.
OL,12,FHe pleaded guilty to a total of 25
OL,13,Foffences which included, 11 counts of
OL,14,Factual bodily harm, six counts of
OL,15,Fcruelty to a child and eight counts of
OL,16,Fadministering prescription only
OL,17,Fmedicines contrary to the law.
OL,19,FDuring his sentencing the court heard
OL,20,Fvictim impact statements from the
OL,21,Ffamilies of a number of children.
