OL,6,FOne said: "Mr Siddiqui came to my home
OL,7,Fwith no PPE, no sterilised equipment
OL,8,Fand not even the items for basic
OL,9,Fhygiene, and using a numbness cream,
OL,10,Fwhich should have been left on for
OL,11,Fsixty minutes but only left on for two
OL,12,Fminutes, Mr Siddiqui carried out a
OL,13,Fsurgical procedure on my son.
OL,15,F"Even now I can remember my son's
OL,16,Fvoice crying out in pain.
