OL,6,F"He was only five weeks old. Due to Mr
OL,7,FSiddiqui's actions my son had to spend
OL,8,Ftwo weeks in hospital and even had to
OL,9,Fgo through a Lumbar Puncture
OL,10,Fprocedure. We didn't know if he was
OL,11,Fgoing to be OK or not."
OL,13,FPolice Staff Investigator Damon
OL,14,FKennard from Hampshire and Isle of
OL,15,FWight Constabulary said: "He appeared
OL,16,Fentirely indifferent to the risk and
OL,17,Fsuffering he was subjecting children
OL,18,Fto and in so doing betrayed the trust
OL,19,Fparents had placed in him to conduct a
OL,20,Fsafe and sanitary circumcision."
